Build and install devel/arm-none-eabi-binutils

In /usr/ports/devel/arm-none-eabi-gcc/Makefile, add the line:
CONFIGURE_ARGS+=        --with-sysroot=/usr/local/arm-none-eabi --enable-multilib --with-float=hard --with-fpu=fpv4-sp-d16 --with-cpu=cortex-m4 --with-mode=thumb --with-endian=little,big

After the line:
.include "${MASTERDIR}/Makefile"

Then build and install devel/arm-none-eabi-gcc
Then build and install devel/arm-none-eabi-newlib
